Here is the Bike Commute Challenge URL - please login and enter your commute data

http://westpower/BikeCommute/

The front page will give your total info as well as your teams info.

Click on your name (below your team on the left you will see your name)
This will show your calendar.
Scroll to the bottom of the calendar and select "Click here".
You need to select an entry for each day of the calendar month.
Go ahead and fill out the weekends and days you are scheduled not in the office.
	ie: if you don't work weekends or have scheduled time out of the office - select "Out of Office".
For the days you have ridden please select either "Both Ways" or "To Work" or "From Work" or "Did not Ride".
You will see the Leader Board to the right w/ current Team Total Miles and Total Trips.

select "Back To Personal Statistics Page" (located at bottom of calendar) - scroll down and you will see your personal stats.


select "Home Page" to see graphs.


Please see your Team Leader for questions.